name: Survive from Smallfish 2
description:
Survive from Smallfish 2 is a FNAF Fangame If you want the other game of this series. Click here. This game is about to survive from Pranoi. The new robot has been activate. It name is Pat. He has target to steal our mask.

How to Survive.

1. Don't run out off battery

2. Wear mask when Pranoi is come.

3. Protect pat by wear the mask.

4. don't run out off oxygen when you are wearing mask. Don't worry, you can turn the A/C units on.
